=head1 DESCRIPTION

Information about a campaign associated with a vehicle.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 CampaignName => Str

The name of a campaign.


=head2 Status => Str

The status of a campaign, which can be one of the following:

=over

=item *

C<CREATED> - The campaign has been created successfully but has not
been approved.

=item *

C<READY> - The campaign has been approved but has not been deployed to
the vehicle.

=item *

C<HEALTHY> - The campaign has been deployed to the vehicle.

=item *

C<SUSPENDED> - The campaign has been suspended and data collection is
paused.

=item *

C<DELETING> - The campaign is being removed from the vehicle.

=back



=head2 VehicleName => Str

The unique ID of the vehicle.



